phrases: Kei, what is wrong with Kuroi?
You let her in, did not you?
You know I am allergic to cats!
Okay, let me ask you then.
You do not have that allergy anymore.
When you were at death's door on that roof,
I had extra elixir so I fixed it for you.
That case was over a month ago!
When I was wearing a mask every night!
It was pretty funny to watch.
You told me it was fine last week!
I am looking for a place for you.
I am more than happy with the one I have got now.
I am doing this for your sake-
A vehicle fled after being stopped by police.
Code 3, head to the scene immediately.
He is going to pay for that!
Jump out if you want to!
Man, you sure made a mess.
Supposedly it was stolen from some warehouse...
And it is all porn magazines?
Nothing about it seems especially strange.
Oh, but this one's pretty hardcore.
But you could never ask your girlfriend to do this.
You have got a boring girlfriend.
They told me to move it, so I moved it.
I have been practicing in secret.
If you just want to move it a little, it is easy-
Can you two guess what I am feeling right now?
You look like you feel sick.
Because you are a pair of dumbass wannabe cowboys!
I have been getting complaints all day thanks to your little car chase stunt!
And not only that, they are telling me we have to take the case!
Now I have to spend resources
to investigate a bunch of porn that could only turn on a middle school kid!
Then what happens to my car?
I kept asking for a car for undercover missions, and you kept ignoring me!
So I had to use my own damn car!
You paired me up with this alien,
and then I took my eyes off her for a second...
She was such a good car!
She was a great partner, always there for me when things got rough!
Throw me in front of a truck!
Then you will be satisfied right?
I will try to find you a new car, so calm down!
There is a police auction coming up!
If there is a good car, I will see if I cannot get it for you!
That is what I wanted to hear, Chief!
It is so wonderful when you have got a good boss!
You are like a little kid begging for a toy.
Anyway, you are in charge of this porn theft case!
It is dumb as hell, but a crime's a crime!
You can ask someone for help if you want.
Honestly, I do not know why anybody would give you a driver's license.
It is like giving Jeffrey Dahmer a license to kill.
Anyway, we need to get started on this porn thing...
In addition to drugs and guns, we also handle prostitution and porno.
Your mom and dad did this stuff!
How dare you insult my mother and father!
That is going too far, even for you!
Then you divided from them, like bacteria.
I think if anything, it makes more sense than the alternative.
Come to think of it, your world does not have a lot of photographs, does it?
I guess porn would be a big shock.
I am not helping you look for porn.
Jamie, I was hoping you could help me with something...
Sorry, Kei, I need to turn in some paperwork.
You are looking as handsome as ever!
I spent 30 minutes picking it out.
That is very kind of you.
But you know, that is kind of a creepy greeting.
Anyway, I was hoping I could get your help...
Sure it is not a bunch of 12-year-olds?
If they could smuggle them there, they would make a fortune.
Most people there do not even have TVs.
Men in every country are idiots!
We are ruled by our genitals.
Good luck in there, Detective McCloud.
Or do you need me to put a bullet into you?
I will take a photo to send to your boyfriend.
Shut up and introduce me to this little thief.
and checked if any of my flock were looking to sell some porn.
I did not say you could sit here!
Stop looking over your damn shoulder.
I am in a hurry to sell it.
I want proof you have got the money.
Are you telling me you think I am broke, kid?
I have been in this business since you were sucking on your mom's tits.
Do not get on my bad side.
I am in a hurry, that is all...
I am a nice guy, you know.
A week ago, he got in a fight with some moron thug,
and ended up eating his eyeballs!
You do not want your eyeballs eaten, do you?
Anyway, let us see the goods.
So that is where we got the idea!
A while back, some nobles there paid a ton for nudes of Miss July!
I want to live a good life too, you know?
I got the biggest boner for Miss July, too.
Those boobs were the best, huh?
That is not what making love is about, you know?
What is important is having two hearts connect!
The more you hate it, the closer your acting gets to perfection.
We have got our next step.
It is in the parking lot.
I liked your old car better.
I am taking it for a drive.
You are going to see Cecil, right?
Okay, press the pedal down slowly.
You could practice driving with Kei, right?
I was a little surprised you came to me.
It is not really bothering me...
I heard you were a friend that Kei trusted, so...
Is that what an ex is?
But I did not think I was talking about us as men and women...
Yes, you are talking about work partners, right?
If he really does not like someone, he shows them no mercy.
What kind of question is that?
I just want him to see me as an equal.
That is why I am practicing driving.
I actually feel really bad about it...
You two are like brother and sister.
A strong-willed little sister and her brother.
Do not tell him I told you this,
She was a really lively girl, I heard.
Maybe he sees some of her in you.
He never said anything about that.
Sorry, I have been riding her hard all night.
It is almost time for that gang of thieves to get here.
I need you all to provide backup.
How did it go with Cecil?
This is what I meant to do!
You are in the wrong lane!
I am starting to get it!
This speed stuff is not bad...
This is what it feels like to be high!
Jump out if you want to!
I did not expect trouble like this.
But never drive like that again.
Do not treat me like baggage!
I do not just mean driving.
If you will not understand that, who will?
I went a little too far before.
I do not think you are useless.
Once it is out of the shop, I will practice with you.
But promise me that next time you will drive safe-
The damage seems to have gotten a bit worse.
But it is still fixable, right?
Like hell it is fixable, you goddamn alien!
I had to deal with the aftermath of that car chase,
and then got in an argument with the real estate guy about your new place...
From now on, this is my room.
You are the second guest I have had, after Kuroi.
Are you still mad about that silly car?
No, it is gone and it is not coming back.
Next time Next time on COP CRAFT.
